# Pre-Admission Health Assessment

**Patient:** {{ patient.full_name|default:"Unknown Patient" }}
**Assessment Date:** {{ submission.created_at|date:"F j, Y"|default:"Date not available" }}

---

## Executive Summary

{% ai "Executive Summary" %}
Based on the comprehensive health history provided below, create a concise executive summary highlighting:
- Overall health status and risk level (low/moderate/high)
- Most significant medical conditions or concerns
- Key anesthetic considerations
- Priority areas requiring clinical attention
- Recommended pre-operative workup or consultations

Context:
Patient Age: {{ patient.age|default:"Unknown" }}
Surgeries: {% if submission.data.surgeries %}{{ submission.data.surgeries|length }}{% else %}0{% endif %} reported
Medications: {{ submission.data.medications|default:"None listed" }}

Keep this to 3-4 sentences maximum.
{% endai %}

---

{% if submission and submission.data %}

## Risk Assessment & Calculations

### Smoking History
{% if submission.data.smoker %}
**Status:** Active/Former Smoker  
**Duration:** {{ submission.data.smoking_years|default:"Not specified" }} years  
**Quantity:** {{ submission.data.cigarettes_per_day|default:"Not specified" }} cigarettes/day  
{% if submission.data.smoking_years and submission.data.cigarettes_per_day %}
**Pack-Years:** ~{{ submission.data.smoking_years }} years × {{ submission.data.cigarettes_per_day }} cigs/day
{% endif %}
{% else %}
**Status:** Non-smoker
{% endif %}

### Cardiac Risk Indicators
**Conditions Identified:**
{% if submission.data.chest_pain_angina %}- Chest Pain/Angina
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.heart_attack %}- History of Heart Attack
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.high_blood_pressure %}- High Blood Pressure
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.congestive_heart_failure %}- Congestive Heart Failure
{% endif %}{% if submission.data.irregular_heartbeat %}- Irregular Heartbeat
{% endif %}{% if not submission.data.chest_pain_angina and not submission.data.heart_attack and not submission.data.high_blood_pressure and not submission.data.congestive_heart_failure and not submission.data.irregular_heartbeat %}
None of the major cardiac indicators reported.
{% endif %}

### Respiratory Risk Indicators
**Conditions:** {% if submission.data.asthma %}Asthma{% endif %}{% if submission.data.copd %}{% if submission.data.asthma %}, {% endif %}COPD{% endif %}{% if submission.data.sleep_apnea %}{% if submission.data.asthma or submission.data.copd %}, {% endif %}Sleep Apnea{% endif %}{% if not submission.data.asthma and not submission.data.copd and not submission.data.sleep_apnea %}None reported{% endif %}  
**Oxygen Support:** {% if submission.data.home_oxygen %}Yes{% elif submission.data.cpap_machine or submission.data.bipap_machine %}CPAP/BIPAP{% else %}None{% endif %}

### Functional Capacity Assessment
{% if submission.data.walk_frequency %}
**Physical Activity:** Walks {{ submission.data.walk_times_per_week|default:"regularly" }} times per week
{% else %}
**Physical Activity:** Limited or not reported
{% endif %}
**Mobility Aids:** {% if submission.data.walker_cane %}Yes{% else %}None{% endif %}  
**Recent Falls:** {% if submission.data.fallen_recently %}Yes (within 3 months){% else %}No{% endif %}  
**ADL Independence:** {% if submission.data.need_help_daily %}Requires assistance{% else %}Independent{% endif %}

### Nutritional Risk
**Weight Loss (6 months):** {{ submission.data.weight_loss|default:"None reported" }}  
**Appetite/Eating Issues:** {% if submission.data.eating_poorly %}Yes{% else %}No{% endif %}

---

## AI-Generated Clinical Analysis

### Cardiovascular System Assessment

{% ai "Cardiovascular Assessment" %}
Analyze the cardiovascular history and provide:
1. Risk stratification for anesthetic management
2. Specific concerns based on reported conditions:
   {% if submission.data.chest_pain_angina %}- Chest pain/angina (frequency: {{ submission.data.chest_pain_frequency|default:"not specified" }}, last: {{ submission.data.chest_pain_last_date|default:"not specified" }}){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.heart_attack %}- Previous MI (date: {{ submission.data.heart_attack_date|default:"not specified" }}){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.high_blood_pressure %}- Hypertension (duration: {{ submission.data.high_blood_pressure_years|default:"unknown" }} years){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.congestive_heart_failure %}- CHF (duration: {{ submission.data.congestive_heart_failure_years|default:"unknown" }} years){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.chest_pain_stairs %}- Exertional symptoms (chest pain with minimal activity){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.pacemaker %}- Pacemaker (date: {{ submission.data.pacemaker_date|default:"not specified" }}){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.aicd %}- AICD (date: {{ submission.data.aicd_date|default:"not specified" }}){% endif %}
3. Recommended cardiac workup or clearance needed
{% endai %}

### Respiratory System Assessment

{% ai "Respiratory Assessment" %}
Evaluate respiratory status and provide:
1. Perioperative respiratory risk level
2. Analysis of breathing conditions:
   {% if submission.data.asthma %}- Asthma{% if submission.data.puffers %} (uses puffers {{ submission.data.puffers_frequency|default:"regularly" }}){% endif %}{% if submission.data.asthma_emergency %}, recent ED visit ({{ submission.data.asthma_emergency_date|default:"date not specified" }}){% endif %}{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.copd %}- COPD{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.sleep_apnea %}- Sleep apnea{% if submission.data.cpap_machine %} (uses CPAP){% endif %}{% if submission.data.bipap_machine %} (uses BIPAP){% endif %}{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.home_oxygen %}- Requires home oxygen{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.breathing_stairs %}- Dyspnea with minimal exertion{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.hospital_shortness_breath %}- Recent hospitalization for SOB (last 6 months){% endif %}
3. Anesthetic implications and ventilation strategy recommendations
{% endai %}

### Neurological & Functional Assessment

{% ai "Neurological Assessment" %}
Assess neurological history and functional status:
1. Neurological risk factors:
   {% if submission.data.stroke %}- History of stroke ({{ submission.data.stroke_date|default:"date not specified" }}){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.mini_stroke %}- History of TIA ({{ submission.data.mini_stroke_date|default:"date not specified" }}){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.seizures_epilepsy %}- Seizure disorder{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.weakness_paralysis %}- Weakness/paralysis ({{ submission.data.weakness_paralysis_specify|default:"not specified" }}){% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.memory_issues %}- Reported memory impairment{% endif %}
2. Functional capacity implications
3. Cognitive concerns for informed consent and post-op care
{% endai %}

### Medication & Anticoagulation Management

{% ai "Medication Management" %}
Review anticoagulation and medication considerations:
1. Bleeding risk assessment:
   {% if submission.data.blood_thinner_aspirin %}- Aspirin{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.blood_thinner_warfarin %}- Warfarin/Coumadin{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.blood_thinner_plavix %}- Plavix{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.blood_thinner_other %}- Other: {{ submission.data.blood_thinner_other|default:"Specified" }}{% endif %}
2. Current medications: {{ submission.data.medications|default:"None listed" }}
3. Perioperative medication management plan
4. Timing for anticoagulation bridging if needed
{% endai %}

### Anesthetic Risk Summary

{% ai "Anesthetic Risk" %}
Provide an integrated anesthetic risk summary:
1. ASA physical status classification estimate with rationale
2. High-risk features identified in this patient
3. Specific anesthetic concerns:
   {% if submission.data.anesthetic_problems_patient %}- Personal history of anesthetic complications: {{ submission.data.anesthetic_problems_patient_specify|default:"not specified" }}{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.anesthetic_problems_relative %}- Family history of anesthetic complications: {{ submission.data.anesthetic_problems_relative_specify|default:"not specified" }}{% endif %}
   {% if submission.data.mouth_neck_difficulty %}- Airway concerns (difficulty opening mouth/moving neck){% endif %}
4. Recommended anesthetic approach (general vs regional vs monitored)
5. Special monitoring or precautions needed
{% endai %}

---

## Detailed Medical History Summary

### General Health Factors

**Lifestyle:**
- Smoking: {% if submission.data.smoker %}Yes ({{ submission.data.smoking_years|default:"?" }} years, {{ submission.data.cigarettes_per_day|default:"?" }}/day){% else %}No{% endif %}
- Alcohol: {% if submission.data.drinks_alcohol %}{{ submission.data.alcohol_weekly|default:"Yes" }}{% else %}No{% endif %}
- Substance Use: {% if submission.data.street_drugs %}{{ submission.data.street_drugs_types|default:"Yes" }}{% else %}No{% endif %}

**Pregnancy Status:** {% if submission.data.pregnant %}Yes - Due: {{ submission.data.due_date|default:"not specified" }}, LMP: {{ submission.data.last_menstrual_period|default:"not specified" }}{% else %}No{% endif %}

**Pain:** {% if submission.data.general_body_pain %}General body pain reported{% endif %}{% if submission.data.ongoing_pain %} Ongoing pain: {{ submission.data.ongoing_pain_location|default:"location not specified" }}{% endif %}{% if not submission.data.general_body_pain and not submission.data.ongoing_pain %}No chronic pain reported{% endif %}

### Cardiovascular History

{% if submission.data.chest_pain_angina or submission.data.heart_attack or submission.data.high_blood_pressure or submission.data.congestive_heart_failure or submission.data.irregular_heartbeat or submission.data.heart_murmur or submission.data.pacemaker or submission.data.aicd or submission.data.heart_surgery or submission.data.angioplasty or submission.data.abnormal_ecg %}
{% if submission.data.chest_pain_angina %}• **Chest Pain/Angina:** Frequency: {{ submission.data.chest_pain_frequency|default:"not specified" }}, Last: {{ submission.data.chest_pain_last_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"not specified" }}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.chest_pain_stairs %}• **Exertional Symptoms:** Chest pain/pressure with ≤2 flights of stairs{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.heart_attack %}• **Myocardial Infarction:** {{ submission.data.heart_attack_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"Date not specified" }}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.high_blood_pressure %}• **Hypertension:** {{ submission.data.high_blood_pressure_years|default:"Duration unknown" }} years{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.congestive_heart_failure %}• **CHF:** {{ submission.data.congestive_heart_failure_years|default:"Duration unknown" }} years{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.irregular_heartbeat %}• **Arrhythmia:** Irregular heartbeat/palpitations{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.heart_murmur %}• **Valvular Disease:** Heart murmur/valve problems{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.pacemaker %}• **Pacemaker:** Implanted {{ submission.data.pacemaker_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"date unknown" }}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.aicd %}• **AICD:** Implanted {{ submission.data.aicd_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"date unknown" }}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.heart_surgery %}• **Cardiac Surgery:** {{ submission.data.heart_surgery_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"Date not specified" }}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.angioplasty %}• **Angioplasty:** {{ submission.data.angioplasty_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"Date not specified" }}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.abnormal_ecg %}• **Abnormal ECG**{% endif %}
{% else %}
No significant cardiovascular history reported.
{% endif %}

### Respiratory History

{% if submission.data.asthma or submission.data.copd or submission.data.sleep_apnea or submission.data.pneumonia or submission.data.tuberculosis or submission.data.breathing_stairs or submission.data.breath_walking or submission.data.hospital_shortness_breath %}
{% if submission.data.asthma %}• **Asthma**{% if submission.data.puffers %} - Uses inhalers {{ submission.data.puffers_frequency|default:"regularly" }}{% endif %}{% if submission.data.asthma_emergency %}, ED visit {{ submission.data.asthma_emergency_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"recently" }}{% endif %}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.copd %}• **COPD** (Emphysema/Chronic Bronchitis){% endif %}
{% if submission.data.sleep_apnea %}• **Sleep Apnea**{% if submission.data.cpap_machine %} - Uses CPAP{% endif %}{% if submission.data.bipap_machine %} - Uses BIPAP{% endif %}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.home_oxygen %}• **Home Oxygen** required{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.breathing_stairs %}• **Exercise Intolerance:** SOB with ≤2 flights stairs{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.breath_walking %}• **Severe Exercise Intolerance:** SOB walking ≤2 blocks{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.hospital_shortness_breath %}• **Recent Hospitalization:** For SOB within last 6 months{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.pneumonia %}• **Pneumonia:** Last treated {{ submission.data.pneumonia_last_treated|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"date unknown" }}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.tuberculosis %}• **Tuberculosis:** Treated {{ submission.data.tuberculosis_date|date:"Y-m-d"|default:"date unknown" }}{% endif %}
{% else %}
No significant respiratory history reported.
{% endif %}

### Hematologic & Anticoagulation

{% if submission.data.bruising_bleeding or submission.data.bleeding_clotting_disorder or submission.data.hemophilia or submission.data.blood_clots_lungs or submission.data.blood_clots_legs or submission.data.blood_thinner_aspirin or submission.data.blood_thinner_warfarin or submission.data.blood_thinner_plavix or submission.data.blood_thinner_other %}
{% if submission.data.bruising_bleeding %}• **Unexplained Bruising/Bleeding**{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.bleeding_clotting_disorder %}• **Bleeding or Clotting Disorder**{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.hemophilia %}• **Hemophilia**{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.blood_clots_lungs %}• **Pulmonary Embolism** (history){% endif %}
{% if submission.data.blood_clots_legs %}• **Deep Vein Thrombosis** (history){% endif %}

**Anticoagulation:**
{% if submission.data.blood_thinner_aspirin %}- Aspirin{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.blood_thinner_warfarin %}- Warfarin/Coumadin{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.blood_thinner_plavix %}- Plavix{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.blood_thinner_other %}- Other: {{ submission.data.blood_thinner_other|default:"Specified" }}{% endif %}
{% if not submission.data.blood_thinner_aspirin and not submission.data.blood_thinner_warfarin and not submission.data.blood_thinner_plavix and not submission.data.blood_thinner_other %}- None{% endif %}
{% else %}
No significant hematologic history or anticoagulation.
{% endif %}

### Endocrine & Metabolic

{% if submission.data.diabetes or submission.data.thyroid_problems %}
{% if submission.data.diabetes %}• **Diabetes:** {% if submission.data.diabetes_management %}{{ submission.data.diabetes_management|join:", " }}{% else %}Management not specified{% endif %}{% endif %}
{% if submission.data.thyroid_problems %}• **Thyroid Disorder:** {{ submission.data.thyroid_problems_specify|default:"Not specified" }}{% endif %}
{% else %}
No significant endocrine conditions reported.
{% endif %}

