### Neurological & Musculoskeletal

{% if submission.data.stroke or submission.data.mini_stroke or submission.data.seizures_epilepsy or submission.data.multiple_sclerosis or submission.data.myasthenia_gravis or submission.data.muscular_dystrophy or submission.data.weakness_paralysis or submission.data.arthritis or submission.data.osteoarthritis or submission.data.rheumatoid_arthritis %}
